data.description: Welcome home to a relaxed pace of life and all the comforts of small-town living, in this adorable three-bedroom charmer in Conrad. The closed-in front porch welcomes guests in out of the cold before entering the home. Step inside and you will find a beautiful built-in buffet, along with the original woodwork throughout the home. On the main level enjoy a spacious living room, formal dining room, kitchen, and nicely updated full bath. Three perfectly situated bedrooms round out the upper level, including a large main bedroom with ample closet space. In the basement, there is an additional room that would make the perfect craft, shop, or recreation room. With a new roof in 2022, maintenance free vinyl siding, and large fenced in backyard with alley access, this well maintained-home is a gem of a find! Schedule a showing today, this one won't last long.
